                     <interp inst="t18490129-478-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 1 half-crown; the money of <persName id="t18490129-name-275" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18490129-name-275" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18490129-name-275" type="surname" value="MARDEN"></interp>
